import * as React from 'react';
import { Button } from 'react-native-web';
import {  Header,         
          HeaderButtonLeft,
          HeaderButtonRight,
          Title,
          Text1,
          Container1,
          Text2,
          Container2,
          Text3,
          Container3,
          Text4,
          Text5,
          Container4,
          Text6,
          Container5,
          Text7,
          Text8,
          Container6,
          Text9,
          Text10
        } 
from './styles';
import { View,Image} from 'react-native';
import { Entypo } from '@expo/vector-icons';
import { Ionicons } from '@expo/vector-icons';


function MealPlannerScreen({navigation}) { 
  return (
    <View style={{background: '#FFFFFF'}}>
      <Header>
        <HeaderButtonLeft>
          <Ionicons name="chevron-back" size={20} color="black" />
        </HeaderButtonLeft>
        <HeaderButtonRight>
          <Entypo name="dots-two-horizontal" size={20} color="#1D1617" />
        </HeaderButtonRight>
        <Title>Meal Planner</Title>
      </Header>
      <Text1>Meal Nutritions</Text1>
      <Container1>
        <Text2>Weekly</Text2>
      </Container1> 
      <Container2>
      </Container2>
      <Text3>Daily Meal Schedule</Text3>
      <Container3>
        <Text4>Check</Text4>
      </Container3>
      <Text5>Today Meals</Text5>
      <Container4>
        <Text6>Breakfast</Text6>
      </Container4>
      <Container5>
        <Text7>Salmon Nigiri</Text7>
        <Text8>Today | 7am</Text8>
      </Container5>
      <Image 
        source={require('../MealPlanner/Vector.png')}
        style={{position: 'absolute',
          width: 90,
          height: 80,
          left: 30,
          top: 481 
        }}
      />
      <Image
        source={require('../MealPlanner/Icon-Bell.png')}
        style={{position: 'absolute',
          width: 16,
          height: 16,
          left: 309,
          top: 513
        }}
      />
      <Container6>
        <Text9>Lowfat Milk</Text9>
        <Text10>Today | 8am</Text10>
      </Container6>
      <Image
        source={require('../MealPlanner/Layer 2.png')}
        style={{position: 'absolute',
          width: 43,
          height: 41,
          left: 54,
          top: 596
        }}
      />
      <Image
        source={require('../MealPlanner/Icon-Bell.png')}
        style={{position: 'absolute',
          width: 16,
          height: 16,
          left: 309,
          top: 608
        }}
      />
      <Image
        source={require('../MealPlanner/Line 52.png')}
        style={{
          position: 'absolute',
          width: 19.8,
          height: 0,
          left: 310,
          top: 609,             
          border: 1,
          color: '#ADA4A5'
        }}
      />
      <Button
        title="Go to Breakfast"
        onPress={() => navigation.navigate('Breakfast')}
      />
    </View>
  );
}
export default MealPlannerScreen;
